high_descs: Move forward to the counter in front.
Pick up the gray knife.
Go around the counter and go to the sink on the opposite side.
Cut the apple on the left of the sink.
Go right to the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the freezer.
Go back to the sink on the left.
Take one piece of the apple.
Go back to the refrigerator
Chill the piece of apple next to the whole apple in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn left to go to the microwave on the counter.
Place the apple inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Step to the right and face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Walk around the counter and across the room to face the sink.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the top shelf of the left side of the fridge.
Step to the left to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Step to the right to face the fridge.
Cool the apple in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the microwave.
Place the piece of apple in the microwave and shut it.
anns.task_desc: To cool a piece of apple and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk towards the counter top to the left.
Pick up the knife that is underneath the fork on the counter top.
Turn right, head towards the door, turn left, then head towards the refrigerator, the left to the stove, turn right towards the sink.
Slice the apple located near the window on the left side of the sink.
Turn right, then head towards the refrigerator,
Open the doors, place the knife in the freezer on the top shelf, then close the doors.
Head towards the microwave, the turn towards the sink.
Pick up the apple from the counter top underneath the window.
Turn right then head towards the refrigerator.
Open the doors, then place the apple slice next to the tomato on the second shelf, then close the doors.
Turn left, head towards the microwave.
Place the apple slice on the blue plate in between the green cup and the egg.
anns.task_desc: Place an apple slice in the microwave on a blue plate.
